Design tokens, principles, component rules, and screen-level rules live in `docs/DESIGN.md`.

Rules:
- Reuse the primitives in `src/components/ui/*` before creating new components.
- Include loading, empty, and error states for data screens.
- Product cards show image, brand, name, SKU, Eazy Score, Community Score, and lowest price.
- Score badges display `No score yet` when the score is null.

Screen UI work follows the routine in `skills/ui-screen-builder/SKILL.md`.
